Description: Cylinder seal of black steatite: perforated through the centre and rather worn on the surface. The seal bears an incised inscription. Good condition.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit III (Wiesbaden, 1964), pl. 103, abb. 468; P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit II (Wiesbaden, 1964), 1154.
